https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/find-last-digit-of-ab-for-large-numbers1936/1
1) using pow:
syntax: pow(base,expo,mod)
class Solution:
    def getLastDigit(self, a, b):
        if b==0:
            return 1
        else:
            c=int(a)
            d=int(b)
            return pow(c,d,10)
            

2) (simple program: high time complexity)
class Solution:
    def getLastDigit(self, a, b):
        c=int(a) 
        d=int(b)
        e=c**d
        return e%10
        
